# UDMF Map Support
*Auto-generated on 2025-09-18*

## Supported Properties

### Vertices
- `x`
- `y`

### Linedefs
- `v1`
- `v2`
- `sidefront`
- `sideback`
- `blocking`
- `twosided`

### Sidedefs
- `sector`
- `texturemiddle`
- `texturebottom`

### Sectors
- `heightfloor`
- `texturefloor`
- `heightceiling`

### Things
- `x`
- `y`
- `height`
- `z`
- `angle`
- `type`

## Notes
- Properties not listed above are not supported
- Position values are scaled by `RendererMain.MasterScale`
